    "7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_KHjEBr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How fast is delivery?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>If you're in the UK we'll have your Chuug made and sent within 2 working days. All parcels are sent by Next Day Delivery, so if you order now you can expect to be holding your Chuug 3 days from now!<br/><br/>If you're outside of the UK, you can expect your order within 10 working days.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_N9F4U8": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I put it in the dishwasher?",
            "icon": "washing",
            "row_content": "<p>A Chuug is scared of nothing. Except dishwashers.<br/>Hand-wash and hand-dry only and it'll last a lifetime. Do not submerge it in water or you're asking for trouble.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_4kna6c": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I put HOT drinks in it?",
            "icon": "fire",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, absolutely. We have designed and built the Chuug with hot drinks in mind. Not only is it insulated to keep drinks warm, but we use heat-resistant materials and adhesives so nothing can get damaged.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--20128198459711__7048141c-2f11-4621-ba5c-28f2f7eaf65e-collapsible_row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you deliver worldwide?",
            "icon": "truck",
            "row_content": "<p>Great news! We are delighted to offer worldwide shipping on all our items.<br/><br/>Whether you're located down the street or across the globe, you can enjoy the convenience of having our exquisite rope handle beer tankards delivered right to your doorstep.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_EgEkFF": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I clean it?",
            "icon": "washing",
            "row_content": "<p>We recommend hand-washing with your usual dish soap, but DO NOT submerge it in water!<br/>The wood exterior is sealed to keep water out, but this is still a natural wood product that needs to be looked after with a conscious effort to not let it sit in water.<br/>Treat it well and it will last a lifetime.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_EDtCrK": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is is made from?",
            "icon": "recycle",
            "row_content": "<p>We exclusively use sustainable Mango Wood and Stainless Steel for the main Chuug body.<br/>The rope handle is made from a patented <strong>SmartRope</strong> which looks and feels like hemp rope but is in fact synthetic so it will not rot, wrap or stretch over time.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "bc2d7b27-4026-4116-aada-d39a7402fe6b": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I pronounce \"Chuug\"?",
            "icon": "chat_bubble",
            "row_content": "<p>CHUG!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
